    dc:title "A checklist of the hawkmoths (Lepidoptera: Sphingidae) of the Cayman Islands: with implications for the pollination of the ghost orchid Dendrophylax fawcettii Rolfe (Orchidaceae: Angraecinae) and consideration of bat predation" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7167947>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7167949> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7167947>
    dc:description "Figures 2–7. Cayman Islands Sphingidae. 2) Isognathus rimosa. 3) Erinnyis obscura. 4) Phryxus caicus. 5) Predation of Pachylia ficus larva by Mangrove Cuckoo, Coccyzus minor. 6) Pachylia ficus. 7) Enyo lugubris. Photographic credits: M.C. Rose-Smyth (2, 27.i.2017; 3, 08.viii.2018; 4, 24.xiii.2015, 6, 05.iv.2018; 7, 13.ii.2018), Yves-Jacques Rey-Millet (5, 29.xii.2012)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7167947/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7167949>
    dc:description "Figures 8–11. Cayman Islands Sphingidae. 8) Eumorpha vitis. 9) Eumorpha fasciatus. 10) Eumorpha satellitia posticatus. 11) Xylophanes tersa. Photographic credits: Stuart Mailer (8, 12.v.2010), Peter and Norma Davey (9, 10.ii.2018), Gary J. Goss (10, 26.vi.2017), M.C. Rose-Smyth (11, NTCI collection)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7167949/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

